{"tid":1702111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"野豬都上前線築路障","createTime":"2019-11-09T14:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T14:23:09.000Z","uid":83582,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a06677662cd955d667f7022e4da5c6c6de08bb7","tid":1702111,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"野豬山頂覓食無果 推垃圾桶出馬路<br />\n11月09日(六) 18:24<br />\n<br />\n今日(9日)下午5時許，有《東網》讀者行經山頂太平山餐廳對開時，發現一頭野豬靜悄悄在行人路上覓食，但一無所獲，牠疑因太飢餓，連路邊的垃圾桶亦不放過，把它推倒，欲伸頭入內尋寶，惟由於垃圾桶口太細，野豬一直都不成功，反而把垃圾桶推出馬路。有駕駛者猶恐撞及野豬，立即停車，另有多名市民舉機拍攝。野豬最終放棄，自行返回附近山邊後，失去蹤影。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191109/photo/bkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001_01b.jpg?20191109190922\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20191109190922&h=90ae33df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191109/photo/bkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001_02b.jpg?20191109190922\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20191109190922&h=c8b09af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191109/photo/bkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001_03b.jpg?20191109190922\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20191109190922&h=4995ffd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191109/bkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191109%2Fbkn-20191109182423752-1109_00822_001.html&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d02923bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191109/bkn-20191